I use an excel spreadsheet to put down stuff i need to keep track of. Personal history, passage of time, it depends on the story you are telling and how relevant backstory is. I'll use another sheet to jot down plot directions, themes and patterns of character development as I think of them. Sometimes if this gets rich enough I'll rewrite the notes into a brief summery in prose to see how it feels narratively.

Its sort of weird because the stuff I've written on 4chan was done on the fly, but i have a lot of mental notes on several other stories that I've planned out but haven't started yet, so I'm not sure how my work flow would change if I had to transcribe a lot of concepts I'm keeping in my head.
